--[[pod_format="raw",created="2026-04-09 17:08:10",modified="2026-04-09 17:14:45",revision=6]]
The concurrency model of Strawberry will be
modeled after Swift as it is very elegant and
on traditional linear memory platforms implementable
very cleanly using a clever calling convention.

On esoteric platforms we can lower continuations
to use fat function pointers and dispatch.
